sentences: He has also won the 2015 Kerala State Film Awards for Best Sound Designer for the movie Ennu Ninte Moideen and 2017 Kerala State Film Awards for Best Sound Designer for the movie Ee.
He has also won the 2015 Kerala State Film Awards for Best Sound Designer for the movie Ennu Ninte Moideen and 2017 Kerala State Film Awards for Best Sound Designer for the movie Ee.

To pursue his passion, he moved to Bollywood in 2006 for more opportunities where he worked as a sound editor with renowned sound designers like Vivek Sachidanand, P. Balaram, Dwarak Warrier and Academy Award winner Resul Pookutty.
It was in 2010, he made his debut as a sound designer in Mollywood for the film Nayakan, directed by Lijo Jose Pellissery.
